<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE article PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook XML V4.5//EN" "http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/4.5/docbookx.dtd">
<article lang="en">
  <title>Formatted Document Test</title>
  
  <section>
    <title>Introduction to Formatting</title>
    <para>This document contains <emphasis role="bold">various</emphasis> types of <emphasis>formatting</emphasis> to test the conversion service's ability to preserve formatting when converting between DOCX and PDF.</para>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <title>Text Styling</title>
    <para>Here are some examples of text styling:</para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem><para><emphasis role="bold">Bold text</emphasis> should be preserved</para></listitem>
      <listitem><para><emphasis>Italic text</emphasis> should be preserved</para></listitem>
      <listitem><para><emphasis role="underline">Underlined text</emphasis> should be preserved</para></listitem>
      <listitem><para>Colored text should be preserved if possible</para></listitem>
      <listitem><para>Text with highlighting should be preserved if possible</para></listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <title>List Formatting</title>
    
    <section>
      <title>Unordered List</title>
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem><para>First item</para></listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>Second item</para>
          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem><para>Nested item 1</para></listitem>
            <listitem><para>Nested item 2</para></listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>
        <listitem><para>Third item</para></listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <title>Ordered List</title>
      <orderedlist>
        <listitem><para>First step</para></listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>Second step</para>
          <orderedlist>
            <listitem><para>Substep a</para></listitem>
            <listitem><para>Substep b</para></listitem>
          </orderedlist>
        </listitem>
        <listitem><para>Third step</para></listitem>
      </orderedlist>
    </section>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <title>Block Elements</title>
    
    <section>
      <title>Blockquote</title>
      <blockquote>
        <para>This is a blockquote that should be preserved with the proper formatting during conversion. The indentation and styling should be maintained as much as possible.</para>
      </blockquote>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <title>Code Block</title>
      <programlisting>
function testFunction() {
  console.log("Hello, world!");
  return true;
}
      </programlisting>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <title>Highlight Block</title>
      <note>
        <para>This is a highlighted block of text that should maintain its background color and border styling during conversion if possible.</para>
      </note>
    </section>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <title>Conclusion</title>
    <para>This document tests the <emphasis role="bold">formatting preservation capabilities</emphasis> of the conversion service. The goal is to maintain as much of the original formatting as possible when converting between DOCX and PDF formats.</para>
  </section>
</article>